data.description: Super bright, flooded with natural light, high ceilings, fantastic open floor plan, 2 bedroom 2.1 bath Town-home located in a quiet Cul-d-sac location in Amber Grove subdivision with an extra long driveway.  Master bedroom has vaulted ceiling and private bath. Kitchen with brand new granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and eating area.  Washer/dryer laundry space. 2 car attached garage. Close to shopping, schools and  parks, entertainment.  MUST SEE!!
